data.description: Discover the hidden gem within this 38.39-acre wooded paradise. This 3-bedroom, 2-bath home is a fixer-upper waiting for your personal touch. Beyond the cosmetic potential, the property boasts a basement offering additional square footage and a detached 2-car garage ready to house your vehicles or serve as a workshop. The wooded acres surrounding the home add a touch of natural serenity to your vision.
